<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4609021>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Morphological variation between males of P. krefftii and P. ambanguluensis. Direct comparisons of characters (abbreviations shown for traits described in the methods section) in P. krefftii (orange) and P. ambanguluensis (blue). For each trait, boxplots show the median, interquartile ranges and overall ranges of measurements, with outliers indicated by circles. Significantly different traits between P. krefftii and P. ambanguluensis after correcting for multiple tests are indicated with an asterisk. PCA analyses of the three species (P. krefftii, P. ambanguluensis, and the single North Pare male (purple)) showing PC1 and PC2 are shown in the bottom right corner. No differences were observed." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4609021/files/figure.png" .

