<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4609037>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Phrynobatrachus krefftii in life from the type locality (Amani Nature Reserve), a) male and female in amplexus, b) male, c) close-up of Phrynobatrachus krefftii eggs, and, d) male, showing bright yellow gular patch. Photos provided by James Vonesh. Non-vouchered specimens." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4609037/files/figure.png" .

